      <title>消息人士称，意大利要求 UniCredit 银行全面披露 BPM 收购事宜</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/italy-demands-full-disclosure-unicredit-over-bpm-bid-sources-say-2024-12-23/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[消息人士称，意大利希望裕信银行按照欧盟政府用来审查战略领域投资的“黄金权力”规则，披露其对较小竞争对手意大利联合银行 (Banco BPM) 的收购提议的全部条款。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/italy-demands-full-disclosure-unicredit-over-bpm-bid-sources-say-2024-12-23/</guid>
